{"tid":2413352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：下周一會率領一眾司局長集體接種科興疫苗，令市民更放心接種","createTime":"2021-02-18T15:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T18:20:46.000Z","uid":350584,"like":40,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e7d46d648e433ce8288edf1a2a234e9b586bf9","tid":2413352,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"消息人士指出，林鄭月娥現時預定於下周一會率一眾司局長，集體接種科興疫苗，時間將定於下午，但未有透露地點。倘市民於下周五開始接種疫苗，意味着林鄭及一眾司局長將早過市民四日接種，含有「示範」作用，接種幾日後無事，市民更放心接種。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jWq88kb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjWq88kb.png&h=18aac5ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aff0638889db77fdf0dab5fd656334ca2daadbeb","tid":2413352,"uid":38703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:34:04.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥 接種疫苗 安全無事集氣區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2413353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2413353</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ffca64cd700092f7182342f0cb7f152656886d01","tid":2413352,"uid":123774,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:34:42.000Z","msg":"死閪婆死撚晒先至會令香港人安心"},{"pid":"d0f347ea88d1617e80f166bda27639d4a0584d3d","tid":2413352,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:34:50.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥今（18日）在facebook表示，下星期開展的疫苗接種計劃，標誌着香港的抗疫工作將進入一個新的里程碑。她又指，早前已表明會接種首款抵港被批准作緊急使用的疫苗，「現在看來，我會『打』的將會是明天抵港在內地研發和生產的科興『滅活技術』新冠疫苗&mdash; Sinovac。」"},{"pid":"37e95c993700aac035b492310d82e219db02cd15","tid":2413352,"uid":103156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:35:08.000Z","msg":"all eggs in one broken basket"},{"pid":"7853cc5aa935f6ef8f977f8e5accb8fc2bf07cbb","tid":2413352,"uid":31237,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"